							<h3>Title: Jane Eyre</h3>
							<h5>Author: Charlotte Bronte</h5>
							<p>Book Description: Maudling and Co, London, 1892. Hard Cover. Fourth Impression. One of only 500 published in this format.  Hard Cover. Fine condition with immaculate wood 
							engravings by Bob Wallis on front cover, and illustrations by Thomas Dury throughout.. Extended introduction by Rebecca Sterns. Slipcase in blue velvet is solid; only very mild 
							scuffing on sides and bottom.  This is a an unsigned copy.</p>
