							<h3>Title: Mill on the Floss</h3>
							<h5>Author: George Eliot</h5>
							<p>Book Description: William Bigwort, Edinburgh, 1860. First Edition. Three octavo volumes; publisher's tan-brown fabric, beautifully embossed in blind and gold lettered on spines;. 
							Cream end pages, with binder's ticket of Eddis & Remartas to the back of volume one. First volume has been expertly restored at corners, otherwise  a remarkable, original and well-preserved 
							collection. Early ownership signature ("Reginald Peters") at beginning of each volume. </p>
						</div>
